{
  "stem": "3012.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were standing naked, s-- preceding-- proceeding from the shower through a long corridor, all naked, stark naked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were waiting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know for what, but we noticed that to the right-- I can see it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean it's here even after 51 years-- a huge hole with ovens, closed-- with ovens with closed doors, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] spotlessly clean.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing at all that you can figure out what's what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We thought, it's, its a bakery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every door was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No smudges, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some prisoners were standing there, which of course later we found out were the members of the Sonderkommando and some SS men.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody uttered a word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And little did we know that in a few hours, this will be the last depository of members of our family and the rest of the convoy people who were put to the-- who were herded to the left.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, again, I have to repeat myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's been 51 years-- it will be 51 on the 15th of June.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's happening now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I see them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then they herded us to yet another room where female prisoners with long brushes wiped us in the front and in the back with some kind of disinfectant, which of course, with the coarse brush, caused lacerations, and it was a burning, nasty sensation.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they gave us some kind of a rag, and we were dismissed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took us-- oh, we couldn't figure out what the smoke is, or what-- eventually it got dark-- what the red flame.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't have the slightest idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The smell, probably burning rubber.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
